Running the script to download all the SRR ids from the project and reformat them into fastq
cat SRR_Acc_List.txt | xargs -n 1 -P 4 ../scripts/download_and_convert.sh 

Running the script that renames the SRR files into their library names
../scripts/rename_SRR_files.sh SRR_to_name.csv fastq_files/

Running a R script in the Bash consol
module restore R
R CMD BATCH script.R R_output.txt

Running tokenized Bert model
python3 train_tokenizer_bert.py -t WORDS -s 20 -r results/WORDS/ -l 6 -a 8 -z 256 -d 3Classes/ -e 20 -p 1000 -y CLASSIFICATION -m 14

Get an interactive GPU node:
interactive --partition=gpua100i --gres=gpu:1 --nodes=1 --ntasks=1 --cpus-per-task=16 --time=02:00:00 -A lu2024-2-56

Get an interactive CPU node:
interactive --cpus-per-task=48 --time=04:00:00 -A lu2024-2-56
